  <h4>Frequently Asked Questions</h4>

  <div class="portletBody portletContent">

    <b>What can I do to help manage the volume of bugmail I receive?</b>
    <p>Every bugmail sent by Malone includes one or more
    <code>X-Launchpad-Bug</code> headers. You can use tools such as
    <a href="http://www.procmail.org">procmail</a> to create custom filters
    based on this header.</p>
